data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house situated on approximately 0.25 acres of well-manicured land. This 1,580 sqft home, built in 2013 has many features that offer both convenience and style.  The kitchen featuring exquisite granite countertops that not only provide ample space for your culinary endeavors but also add an elegant touch to the interior. Whether you're cooking for your family or hosting guests, this kitchen will be a delight.  The master bathroom is a true oasis, complete with a double vanity for your convenience, a jetted tub for relaxation, and a spacious walk-in shower for those refreshing moments. It's the perfect spot to unwind after a long day.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Come and see all the wonderful features this property has to offer.
